• the company offices and worksites;
 • Other buildings or premises under the jurisdiction of the company; 
• Company vehicles;

    • Social functions sanctioned by or under the jurisdiction of the company whether held at company offices or facilities or at other locations approved by the company;

• Work-related travel outside of company facilities; 
• Incidents which occur outside the workplace, but have negative repercussions at work or adversely affect working relationships;

 • Harassment that occurs by electronic means (e-mail, telephone, voice mail, internet, or fax) or written communication; and 

